        .col-xs-12.col-sm-7.col-md-8.col-lg-8.pull-left
          h3 Product Inventory Backlog
          small User stories that are desired but will not be present in release 1.0.
        .col-xs-12.col-sm-12.col-md-12.col-lg-12
          if project
